{"tid":881853,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[Worth It]有冇人睇開Worth It?","createTime":"2018-10-29T17:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T06:31:29.000Z","uid":36296,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ad36c744839f343a0889e816ba9dd18c6af78251","tid":881853,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:46:41.000Z","msg":"相信好多人都有睇過/睇開 但因為見冇人開post討論先開 順便介紹比未睇過既巴絲一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5vtqDuUM1DmXwYYAQcyUwtcalp_SesZD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPL5vtqDuUM1DmXwYYAQcyUwtcalp_SesZD&d=gNd%2FZe%2F%2Ffi2rFZVpg4x76SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=12bd10fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5vtqDuUM1DmXwYYAQcyUwtcalp_SesZD</a><br />\n<br />\n節目介紹：<br />\nWorth It屬於buzzfeed其中一個分支 大約每星期出一集 每集介紹<span style=\"color: red;\">一種</span>食物 會試三間餐廳 三間餐廳既價位都唔同 由平價食到貴價 再選出邊間最worth it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開始只係限於美國餐廳 但之後擴展到澳洲日本等唔同國家 黎緊應該會去新既國家拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成員介紹：<br />\nSteven<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/012611_4ed8fa2027300cd787d073081ffc3161.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F012611_4ed8fa2027300cd787d073081ffc3161.png&h=53ad6a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSteven係馬來裔美國人 呢個節目既靈魂人物 由第一集做到依家 算係幾風趣幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAndrew<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/012831_ba5c84883baec2d3b04af4607107223e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F012831_ba5c84883baec2d3b04af4607107223e.png&h=0a986c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一季中途換入頂上 一直做到依家第五季 成日搞唔好笑既爛gag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同steven經常互串<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAdam<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/013221_64252a8af5ac6ba1a0d412dd6ea6925e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F013221_64252a8af5ac6ba1a0d412dd6ea6925e.png&h=61f14f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同andrew同一時間加入 一直做到依家既cameraman <br />\n成日扮cool既佐助型毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  根據Andrew 佢係off-camera 時候超多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有其他好多客串既BF員工 <br />\n比較常出現既係日本裔既Rie 幫佢地三條友喺日本做翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個節目最好睇既地方係佢地既友誼每日都加深 由唔識焗住一齊拍片到依家感情超好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢個channel 真係buzzfeed清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373c1767e493044277b2ea9332ac39468b5ba396","tid":881853,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:49:56.000Z","msg":"建議大家可以由第一季第三集開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861f83af53587a4ca153914589ced7b68fa35a57","tid":881853,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"373c1767e493044277b2ea9332ac39468b5ba396","tid":881853,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:49:56.000Z","msg":"建議大家可以由第一季第三集開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"尾三pizza片開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8669ca4119ea543ca361085425a5c9c462ed1d48",